text: "No Diggity" is a 1996 new jack swing and rhythm and blues song by Blackstreet. The song reached #1 in the United States and in New Zealand. The song contains rap verses inside it. The rap verses were performed by Teddy Riley and Dr. Dre. ==References== Category:1996 songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Billboard Hot 100 number one songs Category:Billboard Rhythmic Songs number-one singles
title: No Diggity
